
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es-MX">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">

    <title>SADS-Online</title>
  </head>

  <body>

    <div class="container">
      <nav class="navbar navbar-light ">
        <button class="navbar-toggler hidden-sm-up" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#exCollapsingNavbar2">&#9776;</button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-toggleable-xs" id="exCollapsingNavbar2">
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"><h2 class="text-muted">Sistema Administrador de Donaciones de Sangre</h2></a>
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav pull-xs-right">
            <li class="nav-item active">
              <%= link_to 'Inicio', root_path, class:"nav-link" %>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#">Ingresa</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#">Registrate</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <%= link_to 'Publica', new_post_path, class:"nav-link" %>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <hr/>

      <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1 class="display-3">Necesitas un donante?</h1>
        <p class="lead">Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.</p>
        <p><%= link_to 'Publica', new_post_path, class:"btn btn-lg btn-success" %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-offset-1 col-lg-10">
          <p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6" style="text-align:center;">
          <h1>Todas las publicaciones</h1>
          <hr/>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <% @posts.each do |post| %>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4" style="margin-top:20px;">
          <hr class="post">
          <h2 class="post-name"><%= post.post_name %></h2>
          <p class="message"><%= post.message %></p>
          <p><%= link_to 'Ver publicación »', show_post_path(post), class:"btn btn-secondary" %></p>
        </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <hr/>

      <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; Company 2014</p>
      </footer>

    </div> <!-- /container -->


    <!-- Bootstrap core JavaScript
    ================================================== -->
    <!-- Placed at the end of the document so the pages load faster -->
    <!-- IE10 viewport hack for Surface/desktop Windows 8 bug -->
  </body>
</html>